tannery
Discworld player help
tannery

.SH Name
.SI 5
tannery - a place where you can fix your leather belongings.
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
If you are competent enough in tanning to have the 'leatherwork' command,
you can make use of the facilities in this room to repair your leather
goods.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> leatherwork cost black leather trousers
To attempt to repair the pair of black leather trousers, it would probably
cost you about A$3.15.
> leatherwork black leather trousers
You manage to sew up some of the holes in the pair of black leather
trousers but a few pop back open due to poor stitching.
The thread and sinew costs you A$3.15.

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
leatherwork
.EP
